Dialogs.Dialog: By the way, the tests are coming up. Have you been studying？ Hey, how about a review session at my house？
You already know what will be covered in the tests, right？ Um, how about we review the lessons together in my room？
I'm not in the mood today
Have you studied for the tests？ If you have anything you don't understand, Manaka-sensei can teach you.
Okay. When you're ready, just come to my house.
Hehe. That's good. I'll be waiting then.
Hehe. Very well. Let's do this after school.
I see. Too bad... Then maybe next time.
I see. Sorry, I wasn't aware that you weren't in the mood. Maybe next time.
Hmm. Very confident in yourself, huh？ This time, we study on our own then.
▲主人公＊▲. Nice timing. Hey, how about we review the lessons together after this？ What do you think？
Right. The tests are coming up...
▲主人公＊▲. What a coincidence. Hey, if you have time, how about we study for the tests together？
▲主人公＊▲. I was about to call you. Hey, wanna study together？
Ah, the tests are coming up. Let me see...
Really？ Hehe, I'm glad. Then I'll wait at home. Get ready and come see me, okay？
Hehe, I'm glad. Then I'll be waiting at home. See you later.
Yeah, Let's do that！ Well... I'll see you at my house, okay？
I see... Then I might ask you later. Bye now.
Ah... I see. Let's wait until the next chance then. Bye now.
Eh？ Hehe. Too bad... Next time, make yourself available, okay？
I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
Is that so？ Then, you can come study at my house.
I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
Okay, let's study at my house.
I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
Well, how about I tutor you at my house？
Um... Well... Please make yourself at home...
(Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s nervousness makes me feel nervous too...)
This is the first time I invited a guy to my room. I'm so nervous.
Let's concentrate and study hard, okay？
I hope we can review a lot of lessons today.
I hope we can get some good results today.
Um, I feel embarrassed so please don't look around too much.
Don't look over there. Hehe, you helpless guy.
Ah, you're looking again. Are you that curious about a girl's room？ Geez.
Coffee, iced tea, hot tea, water. What do you like？ Hehe.
Have a seat. Shall we start？
Okay, here you are. Make yourself at home.
Okay, I'll ask questions. If you answer them all correctly, I'll give you a reward. Do your best.
Hmm... If you stop and think about it, you'll finally get it.
Hey, you need to be more serious about reviewing your lessons.
Are you ready for the next question？
Yes, you did very well. I'll give you a reward.
Hehe, I expected as much. Now, here's a reward... okay？
Hehe. Great job▼ As I promised, I'll give you a reward.
Disappointing, huh？ Just a little more, and you'll get the reward, okay？
How disappointing... I'm sorry. I won't give you the reward...
Too bad！ You were so close to getting the reward.
...I see. If that's what you want, it's fine.
Hey... I can't give you a reward for this.
Are you not feeling well？ Are you okay？
I wanted to give you a reward, but... Are you serious about this？
That's the spirit. Hehe, do your best.
...Hey, then you don't want to study, huh？
...Hey. Then I'll give you a bonus. This is specially for you, okay？
Can I move closer to you？
I can wear this specially for you, okay？
Hey, how is it？ If you like it, I'll be very happy...
This is what you gave me as a present... Hey, don't ever tell anyone, okay？
I want you to see this... Does it suit me？
...Do you like this？ Let me know.
I hope you like it... But, do I look bad in this？
Time's up, I guess..... Hah, I'm still so nervous.
It's enough, okay？ I did something quite extreme. I'm so embarrassed.
Hehe, that's all. I was really nervous...
Hey, wanna try another round？ I'll reward you with a different costume...
...Okay. Then I'll be looking forward to the next time, okay？
You did a great job. Here's something special for you.
You really did your best, so I should do my part too...
If you don't feel motivated to study, I'll be very angry...
Do you feel motivated？ It's embarrassing, but if it's for you...
This is very embarrassing. But, if it will help motivate you to study, I guess it's okay.
Hey, um... What do you think？
What should I do？ I can't be calm...
Are you just going to keep quiet？
...Hey, can you look away for a while？ Okay...？
If you look at me like that...
Don't look at me like that. It's embarrassing...
Don't look at me with that face. You idiot...
This is probably different from my usual outfits. I'm getting so nervous.
...Are you going to hate me if I continue wearing this？
Okay, this is it for today.
With this, you'll get good test results for sure.
You did perfectly, huh？ Hehe, it's true.
With this, you can rest assured. I wonder if this was worth the effort teaching you. Just kidding.
It wasn't bad but... Shouldn't you put some more effort？
I think you can do a little better than this. Try harder, okay？
Hm, you'd better try harder, okay？
You should study harder... No, I guess I just feel a bit uneasy.
Um... I think you should be more serious when you study.
It's already this late... I think we should stop here...
Hey, what's after this？ Going home？
Really？ Then, can you wait for me just a bit？
Thanks for today. I'm glad I was able to study with you.
I'm so glad too. Thank you.
I'm sorry, I wasn't able to concentrate much...
We had such a strange study session, eh？
Doing something like this is good every once in a while, right？
